import "./c.css" export default function C1() { return (

Think about yourself

  • People aren’t sitting around thinking about you, Most people spend most time thinking about themselves about their own problems, challenges and opportunities
  • Begin today by thinking about your own dreams and the future that desperately awaits your arrival
  • Stop worrying about what others are thinking
  • Stop dreaming, thinking and talking about success and start achieving it
  • The most important ingredient that determines whether a person succeeds is the power of believing in himself
  • Ultimately its not the external circumstances that limit you: It is you, your negative thoughts, comfort zones, self defeating habits, poor strategies, blame lists and failure to continuously educate and grow
  • Your past doesn’t have to equal your future, you can change your life today
  • Achieving is not merely about accumulating life's pleasantries it is about becoming all that you possibly can and then contributing in a positive way
  • Stop seeking approval of others and begin achieving your goals and living your dreams
) }
